[Verse 2]
Main dil da bheda ni mainu maar na tanne
Miliya main pehli wari tenu show de bahane
Hor vi diwane tere piche jag to begane
Tenu dujeya de geet sunande
Main piche piche teri chal vehna aana
Tere gunn gana likhna tere vaaste geet
Tenu bhul jawan ya ban jawan main tera mee
Mainu lab de nai hun koi raaste...
Tere vaaste soniye likhna main geet
Tu bann meri meet kar amar ae preet
Desiyan di reet rag rag ch preet jo tu mange
Oh main kara tere vaaste
Jag di chinta chad aapan dovein fatafat jhat mangni viyah fata fat bina khat pat
Kariye navi zindagi shuru je de ve mera sath tu....

